# FundFit environment example
#
# The MVP runs ENTIRELY on local mock data and needs NO environment variables.
# This file documents variables that future, opt-in integrations might use.
# Copy to `.env.local` and fill in only when you actually wire up an integration.
# NEVER commit real secrets, API keys, or private nonprofit data.

# --- App ---
# Public base URL of the app (used by some integrations / metadata).
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL="http://localhost:3000"

# --- Future: real data sources (NOT used yet) ---
# ProPublica Nonprofit Explorer is currently key-less; placeholder for future use.
# PROPUBLICA_API_BASE="https://projects.propublica.org/nonprofits/api/v2"

# Grants.gov / Simpler Grants API (future)
# GRANTS_GOV_API_KEY=""
# SIMPLER_GRANTS_API_KEY=""

# Candid / Foundation Directory-style data (only if licensed) (future)
# CANDID_API_KEY=""

# --- Future: LLM drafting layer (NOT used yet) ---
# The grant-asset generators are template-based today. To add an LLM later,
# wire one of these in behind the existing generator interface.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""
# LLM_MODEL="claude-sonnet-4-6"
